headline: Add colors and user-configurable backtrace limit
body:
This adds colors (which match GDB's output) to files / symbols when printing exceptions from C++ if stdout is a terminal. This also adds an environment variable `TVM_BACKTRACE_LIMIT` which can be used to limit the length of backtraces at runtime. The combo of these two helps make backtraces easier to read at a glance.

```bash
export TVM_BACKTRACE_LIMIT=5
python some_code_with_an_error.py
```
author: driazati
pr_title: Add colors and user-configurable backtrace limit

headline: [microNPU][3] Plan generation for the cascader
body:
The cascader creates 'Plans' which describe how
to schedule subgraphs. As part of the cascading
algorithm, it's necessary to explore a large
variety of Plans which are Pareto optimal (in
terms of memory usage and performance). This is
done by the Plan generation algorithm.

This commit adds the TensorConfig and Plan data
structures which hold information on how to schedule
the tensors/operators. Additionally, it includes
functions to calculate Pareto frontiers which are
used to cull sub-optimal Plans.

Change-Id: Ia358b2a1b29bd810df4441027752ced75812ad4e
author: mbaret
pr_title: [microNPU][3] Plan generation for the cascader

headline: [microNPU][2c] Initial Performance Model
body:
* Added the pre-computed performance modelling per block.
* Added the aggregation of cycles given a stripe config.
* Implemented the op-specific performance code for conv2d.
* Created a DeviceConfig class to hold constant performance related data
that is dependent on the accelerator configuration
* Added generation of all valid block configs. This is pre-computed and
given as an argument when constructing EthosuParts.
* Implemented selection of the block config that gives the least amount
of data read given a StripeConfig.

Change-Id: Ie5ffff7493e542e8839776f6ac3e0794f4092ea6
author: jacobbohlin
pr_title: [microNPU][3] Plan generation for the cascader

headline: [microNPU][2d] Add more Part matchers for the cascader
body:
Adds Part matchers for ethosu_depthwise_conv2d,
ethosu_pooling and ethosu_binary_elementwise. Also
adds additional testing for the CascaderGraph
creation.

Co-authored-by: Jacob Bohlin <jacob.bohlin@arm.com>
author: mbaret
pr_title: [microNPU][3] Plan generation for the cascader
